nnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"A “planned” transition involving the exits of two sales leaders is also rattling investors.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/mongodbs-stock-sinks-after-earnings-signaling-more-tough-times-for-the-software-sector-5dd37daa\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772501280, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"SoFi’s stock rises as CEO Anthony Noto reacts to recent selloff with a $1 million purchase\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580315, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Noto, who already owns a SoFi stake worth about $215 million on paper, has been known to buy the dip before.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/sofis-stock-rises-as-ceo-anthony-noto-reacts-to-recent-selloff-with-a-1-million-purchase-d03ba5b6\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772492460, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"How this under-the-radar U.S. natural-gas exporter could capitalize on a potential shortage in Europe\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580299, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"The U.S. is the world’s largest exporter of liquefied natural gas, and one relatively obscure U.S. company seems ready to reap the benefits of a surge in global natural-gas prices following the U.S. and Israel’s attacks on Iran and the widening conflict in the Middle East.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/how-this-under-the-radar-u-s-natural-gas-exporter-could-capitalize-on-a-potential-shortage-in-europe-c6938bab\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772490900, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"The smartest money moves to make as the Iran conflict rattles markets\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580298, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"You may have opportunities to optimize for short-term volatility, financial planners told MarketWatch.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/the-smartest-money-moves-to-make-as-the-iran-conflict-rattles-markets-d8e57ef3\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772488020, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"As global markets tanked over Iran, U.S. stocks were mostly unscathed. Here’s why.\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580291, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"There is an old saying in markets: Buy when the bullets (or bombs or missiles) fly.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/as-global-markets-tanked-over-iran-u-s-stocks-were-mostly-unscathed-heres-why-92dc87c5\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772487960, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Gold just passed its stress test — what happens next will tell investors if they’re right\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580292, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Gold did exactly what it was supposed to after the Iran strike. Is the spike temporary or a new era for the safe-haven trade?\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/gold-just-passed-its-stress-test-what-happens-next-will-tell-investors-if-theyre-right-35de6d2f\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772487600, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Iran conflict unlikely to hurt U.S. economy or boost inflation — but the Fed won’t be quick to cut rates\\