c.com/2026/03/02/mortgage-rates-jump-sharply-higher-after-iran-strikes-reversing-last-weeks-decline.html\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772475120, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"EchoStar’s business deemed ‘irrelevant’ as investors focus on future SpaceX stake\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580230, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"The satellite-communications company is essentially a hedge fund with a SpaceX stake, in the view of MoffettNathanson analysts.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/echostars-business-deemed-irrelevant-as-investors-focus-on-future-spacex-stake-5a89c0c7\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772474760, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Most Americans are oblivious to the fact their Social Security checks could be slashed 20% in as soon as 6 years\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580231, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Would an education campaign help workers or cause panic?\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/most-americans-are-oblivious-to-the-fact-their-social-security-checks-could-be-slashed-20-in-as-soon-as-6-years-aded9dd0\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772474131, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Trump says the U.S. is 'richer and stronger than ever'—why some Americans don't feel it\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580232, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108269704-1771998597707-gettyimages-2262903854-AFP_98UU9KZ.jpeg?v=1771998620&w=1920&h=1080\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"CNBC\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"President Donald Trump touted economic wins during his State of the Union address. But Americans and economists say affordability is s