p to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 660.49,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.973\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.news.retrieve.v1.fe8bf94c\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Financial News\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns the latest financial news headlines and full articles for a given ticker symbol or topic tag. Requires either a ticker (s) or a tag (t). Supports filtering by date, pagination, and JSON response format.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The ticker code to retrieve news for, for example: AAPL.US\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"t\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The topic tag to retrieve news for, for example: technology\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Number of results to return (default: 50, minimum: 1, maximum: 1000)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"offset\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Offset for pagination (default: 0)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"fmt\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format, either json or xml (default: json)\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {}\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1.183,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.741\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment Trending\",\n      \"description\": \"This API returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from a large & growing selection of premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and a wide range of topics such as fiscal policy, mergers & acquisitions, IPOs, etc.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function of your choice. In this case, function=NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The stock/crypto/forex symbols of your choice. For example: tickers=IBM will filter for articles that mention the IBM ticker; tickers=COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD will filter for articles that simultaneously mention Coinbase (COIN), Bitcoin (CRYPTO:BTC), and US Dollar (FOREX:USD) in their content.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The news topics of your choice. For example: topics=technology will filter for articles that write about the technology sector; topics=technology,ipo will filter for articles that simultaneously cover technology and IPO in their content. Below is the full list of supported topics: Blockchain: blockchain, Earnings: earnings, IPO: ipo, Mergers & Acquisitions: mergers_and_acquisitions, Financial Markets: financial_markets, Economy - Fiscal Policy (e.g., tax reform, government spending): economy_fiscal, Economy - Monetary Policy (e.g., interest rates, inflation): economy_monetary, Economy - Macro/Overall: economy_macro, Energy & Transportation: energy_transportation, Finance: finance, Life Sciences: life_sciences, Manufacturing: manufacturing, Real Estate & Construction: real_estate, Retail & Wholesale: retail_wholesale, Technology: technology.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format. For example: time_from=20220410T0130. If time_from is specified but time_to is missing, the API will return articles published between the time_from value and the current time.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"By default, sort=LATEST and the API will return the latest articles first. You can also set sort=EARLIEST or sort=RELEVANCE based on your use case.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"By default, limit=50 and the API will return up to 50 matching results. You can also set limit=1000 to output up to 1000 results.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 883.34,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.946\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"37c14cea-4f35-4f61-b302-ff61681b1f30\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 184.13\n}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772534019699}}
{"type":"message","id":"c4243b9d","parentId":"2a84af88","timestamp":"2026-03-03T10:33:55.838Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found Alpha Vantage news sentiment API which might have sentiment/scores. But the user specifically asked for Finnhub. Let me check if Finnhub has any additional fields or a different endpoint that provides hotness. Let me also try getting more details about the news.\n\nActually, looking at the Finnhub response again, I notice that there's no \"hotness\" or \"heat\" field in the response. The user might be referring to a concept I'm not aware of, or they might be mistaken about Finnhub having such a field.\n\nLet me try to get more detailed information about Finnhub's news API by executing the tool and seeing all available fields. Or maybe I should just summarize the top news and explain there's no hotness metric available.\n\nActually, wait - the user specifically said \"【禁止浏览器】只使用QVeris finnhub财经新闻。热度≥80推送给用户。\" This suggests they want me to filter by some hotness metric ≥ 80. Let me check if maybe there's another field or if I need to interpret this differently.\n\nLooking at the news data again, the \"id\" field is just an incremental ID, not a hotness score. There's no hotness metric.\n\nGiven the constraints, I should:\n1. Inform the user that Finnhub news doesn't have a \"热度\" (hotness) metric\n2. Provide the top headlines anyway\n\nOr maybe \"热度≥80\" is a requirement the user has for filtering - perhaps it's a threshold for engagement or importance that doesn't exist in Finnhub's API. Let me check if there's any way to get this data or if I should just present the most important/breaking news.\n\nActually, let me try another approach - maybe there's a different tool that provides news with hotness scores. But the user specifically said \"只用QVeris finnhub\" so I should stick with Finnhub.\n\nLet me just present the top news items and explain that Finnhub doesn't provide hotness scores, so I'm presenting the latest \"top news\" category which seems to be the most prominent/important news.","thinkingSignature":"8dac1aaf54739022ed17b349917c1149eb36359f97f62ed426346d9ad9e5dbf9"},{"type":"text","text":"Finnhub新闻数据中**没有\"热度\"字段**，仅包含: category, datetime, headline, id, image, related, source, summary, url。\n\n当前热门财经新闻 (按最新时间排序):\n\n1. **JPMorgan's Jamie Dimon警告市场过度自满** - MarketWatch\n2. **伊朗冲突影响市场** - 油价飙升、股市动荡\n3. **Gold突破压力测试** - 避险功能显现\n4. **Nvidia获评级上调** - CNBC\n5. **Mortgage利率大幅上升** - CNBC\n6. **Chevron股价创历史新高** - 受油价上涨推动\n7. **Apple发布新版iPhone和iPad Air** - 布局AI战略\n8. **HBO Max与Paramount+将合并** - 流媒体市场整合\n\n**问题**: Finnhub API不提供热度/popularity评分。如需按热度筛选，可能需要使用其他数据源(如Alpha Vantage的sentiment数据，或社交媒体热门话题)。\n\n需要我换用其他提供热度指标的数据源吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":24764,"output":644,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39392,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772534019701}}
